Who's News:
   Bic Corp.'s Bruno Bich
   Is Named Chairman,
   Succeeding His Father
Marcel Bich said that relinquishing his duties in the U.S.
will allow him more time to prepare his son to succeed him at
Societe Bic S.A., which owns 63% of Bic Corp.
   Bic said the special dividend and its quarterly dividend
of 28 cents a share are both payable Feb. 3 to shares of
record Jan. 23. Bic previously paid a $1 special dividend in
May 1990. It currently has about 11.8 million shares
outstanding.
   Bic shares closed yesterday at $31.50, up $1.125, in
American Stock Exchange composite trading.